OL,3,CPolice charge man over series of 'anti-
OL,4,CMuslim' attacks in Edinburgh
OL,6,FPolice Scotland said a 36-year-old man
OL,7,Fhas been charged in connection with a
OL,8,Fseries of attacks in Edinburgh that
OL,9,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,10,Fappeared to be motivated by "anti-
OL,11,FMuslim hatred".
OL,13,FCounter-terrorism officers were
OL,14,Fbrought in to investigate the attacks
OL,15,Facross Edinburgh on Friday which left
OL,16,Ffive people injured.
OL,18,FThe force said on Saturday a white
OL,19,FScottish man had been arrested.
OL,26,@rD@]OUsD@NO]
