OL,3,CPolice charge man over series of 'anti-
OL,4,CMuslim' attacks in Edinburgh
OL,6,FIt said late on Saturday night: "A 36-
OL,7,Fyear-old man has been charged in
OL,8,Fconnection with a number of incidents
OL,9,Fwhich took place in Edinburgh on
OL,10,FFriday, 19 June, 2026.
OL,12,F"A report has been submitted to the
OL,13,FProcurator Fiscal, and the individual
OL,14,Fwill appear at court in due course."
OL,16,FSir Keir earlier on Saturday posted on
OL,17,FX, linking to an image of a bare-
OL,18,Fchested man carrying a large weapon,
OL,19,Fsaying: "Absolutely appalling. No one
OL,20,Fshould face violence on our streets.
OL,26,@nD@aOUtD@AOUvD@dO]{D@IOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
