OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782047474
OL,3,CPolice charge man over series of 'anti-
OL,4,CMuslim' attacks in Edinburgh
OL,6,F"The suspect appears to be motivated
OL,7,Fby anti-Muslim hatred. I will not
OL,8,Ftolerate this ` he will face the full
OL,9,Fforce of the law.
OL,11,F"My thoughts are with those who are
OL,12,Finjured and I thank the police and the
OL,13,Femergency services for their response."
OL,15,FFootage posted online showed a bare-
OL,16,Fchested white man roaming the streets
OL,17,Fof Edinburgh with a large weapon and
OL,18,Fwhile another clip seems to show a man
OL,19,Fbattering the door of a pizzeria.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@gO]
