OL,3,CPolice charge man over series of 'anti-
OL,4,CMuslim' attacks in Edinburgh
OL,6,FPolice closed off Leith Walk on Friday
OL,7,Fevening as the incidents unfolded and
OL,8,Fanother video appeared to show a
OL,9,Ftopless man on the ground shouting
OL,10,Fthat he is "protecting the country" as
OL,11,Fhe is held by an officer.
OL,13,FScottish First Minister John Swinney
OL,14,Falso condemned the violence in an
OL,15,Fonline post on X, saying: "I am deeply
OL,16,Fconcerned by these incidents.
OL,26,@rD@LOUrD@cO]wD@[OU
