OL,3,CPolice charge man over series of 'anti-
OL,4,CMuslim' attacks in Edinburgh
OL,6,F"There is no place for violence,
OL,7,Fracism or intolerance in our country.
OL,8,FI met community groups last week to
OL,9,Fassure them of the strong support of
OL,10,Fthe Government."
OL,12,FOfficers were called to a report of an
OL,13,Fincident in the Sighthill area of the
OL,14,Fcity, where two men were injured, at
OL,15,Faround 8.50pm on Friday.
OL,17,FPolice said they then received reports
OL,18,Fabout incidents around retailers
OL,19,Facross the west and north of the city.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
