OL,3,CPolice charge man over series of 'anti-
OL,4,CMuslim' attacks in Edinburgh
OL,6,FThe force said that during this period
OL,7,Fthree other men were allegedly
OL,8,Fattacked in the Telford Road and Leith
OL,9,FWalk area.
OL,11,FPolice said that five men ` two aged
OL,12,F22, and others aged 24, 27, and 39 `
OL,13,Fsustained a range of injuries. Three
OL,14,Fneeded hospital treatment, although
OL,15,Fnone of the injuries are life-
OL,16,Fthreatening.
OL,18,FSeveral of the victims are Muslim,
OL,19,Faccording to the Muslim Engagement and
OL,20,FDevelopment (Mend) organisation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
