OL,3,CPolice charge man over series of 'anti-
OL,4,CMuslim' attacks in Edinburgh
OL,6,FPolice said a 36-year-old man was
OL,7,Fdetained at around 9.30pm on Friday.
OL,9,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood said
OL,10,Fshe was "horrified" by the violence,
OL,11,Fwhich appeared "to be motivated by
OL,12,Fanti-Muslim hatred", while Police
OL,13,FScotland Assistant Chief Constable
OL,14,FCatriona Paton said it was a
OL,15,F"shocking" and her thoughts are with
OL,16,Fthose who were injured and most
OL,17,Fdirectly affected.
OL,26,@rD@IOUrD@SO]sD@POUtD@SO]wD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
