OL,3,CPolice charge man over series of 'anti-
OL,4,CMuslim' attacks in Edinburgh
OL,6,FMs Mahmood said she was "grateful" to
OL,7,Fthe police and emergency services for
OL,8,Ftheir "bravery in apprehending the
OL,9,Fsuspect and for their speedy response
OL,10,Fin attending to the victims".
OL,12,FShe added: "There is no place for
OL,13,Fhatred and violence against Muslims. I
OL,14,Fknow it is not who we are as a
OL,15,Fcountry."
OL,26,@nD@YOUnD@bO]pD@GOUrD@\O]tD@LOUwD@IO]
