OL,3,CPolice charge man over series of 'anti-
OL,4,CMuslim' attacks in Edinburgh
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Paton said:
OL,7,F"I want to send a clear message of
OL,8,Fsupport to all our communities that
OL,9,Fthere is no place for racism or faith-
OL,10,Fbased hate in a Scotland which is at
OL,11,Fits best when we stand together.
OL,13,F"Officers responded to multiple
OL,14,Freports of a fast-moving sequence of
OL,15,Fevents across Edinburgh before
OL,16,Farresting a man and public safety was
OL,17,Four priority.
OL,19,F"Extensive work is ongoing to
OL,20,Festablish all the circumstances."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
