OL,3,CPolice charge man over series of 'anti-
OL,4,CMuslim' attacks in Edinburgh
OL,6,FThe force is working with Counter
OL,7,FTerrorism Policing and under the
OL,8,Fdirection of the Crown Office and
OL,9,FProcurator Fiscal Service.
OL,11,FShe added: "I want to thank our
OL,12,Fofficers who responded with bravery
OL,13,Fand professionalism, and with a focus
OL,14,Fon protecting the public.
OL,16,F"I'm hugely grateful for the support
OL,17,Fand assistance of our communities and
OL,18,Fwould appeal for anyone with any
OL,19,Finformation to share it with police."
OL,26,@sD@LOUxD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
