OL,3,CPolice charge man over series of 'anti-
OL,4,CMuslim' attacks in Edinburgh
OL,6,FA Major Incident Public Portal (MIPP)
OL,7,Fhas been set up to encourage members
OL,8,Fof the public to submit information
OL,9,Fdirectly to officers.
OL,11,FPolice are appealing to anyone with
OL,12,Finformation that could assist with
OL,13,Finquiries to upload it using an online
OL,14,Fform.
OL,16,FScottish Government's Justice
OL,17,FSecretary Neil Gray said: "These
OL,18,Fattacks were awful and my thoughts are
OL,19,Fwith those who were injured and
OL,20,Faffected by them.
OL,26,@yD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782047474
OL,3,CPolice charge man over series of 'anti-
OL,4,CMuslim' attacks in Edinburgh
OL,6,F"As Police Scotland have said, there
OL,7,Fis no place for racism or faith-based
OL,8,Fhate in Scotland.
OL,10,F"They have also confirmed that a man
OL,11,Fhas been arrested, there is no threat
OL,12,Fto the public and their inquiries are
OL,13,Fongoing. I encourage anyone with
OL,14,Finformation to contact the police.
OL,16,F"This was clearly a very serious
OL,17,Fincident and my thanks go to the
OL,18,Femergency services for their bravery
OL,19,Fand skill in bringing the incident
OL,20,Funder control."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU|D@OO]
